OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEnergy bills: Homes could  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbe heated by floodwater    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffrom disused mines         
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Wales' disused coal mines could get a  
OL,6, new lease of life as a green energy    
OL,7, source to heat homes.                  
OL,9,FInvestigations will be carried out to  
OL,10,Ffind the best spots to pump naturally  
OL,11,Fheated water from underground to       
OL,12,Fcommunities.                           
OL,14,FThe Welsh government is spending       
OL,15,F#450,000 on the project which it hopes 
OL,16,Fwill help cut energy bills and Wales'  
OL,17,Fcarbon footprint.                      
OL,19,FWhen Wales' pits closed, the pumps were
OL,20,Fswitched off and the mines flooded.    
